        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                
            </div>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following incipits are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet128">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 128</ref> according to
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/QZH8VYBF"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><title level="m">Bybliothecae apostolicae Vaticanae codices manu scripti recensiti iussu Pii XI Pontificis maximi. Codices Aethiopici Vaticani et Borgiani, Barberinianus orientalis 2, Rossianus 865&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; Enarratio codicum</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sylvain</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Grébaut</t:surname></author><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Eugène</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Tisserant</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Città del Vaticano</pubPlace><publisher>In Bybliotheca Vaticana</publisher><date>1935</date><citedRange unit="page">480–482, 506–507</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="table1">
                    <label>Divinatory table</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>The table is divided into sixteen columns and seven orders. Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ፩<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> አላህያን፡ በዕል፡ ዕለት። በመጋቢት፡ በ ፳፱<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied>
                            <choice><sic>ይሠርቀ</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut">ይሠርቅ፡</corr></choice> ፳፫<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ያበርህ፡ ዕለት፡ 
                            <surplus>ዕለት፡</surplus> ቤተ፡ ፀሩ፡ አልኬድ፡ ፪፭፮፯፲ ወ ፩፲ ወ፪<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ቤተ፡ ክፍሉ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied>
                            ፩፫፬፰፱፲ወ፬፲ወ፭ወ፲ወ፮<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ኮከቡ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> እልመሸተሪ፡ ዕለ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">ቱ፡
                                ሐ</t:supplied> <t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">ሙስ፡</t:supplied>
                        </ab>
                    </div>                    
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="table2">
                    <label>Astronomical-divinatory table</label>   
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>The table contains the names of the sixteen constellations of the previous table and some directives on their use.
                            Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ለፋል፡ ዘይትገደፍ፡ ለ<add place="above">ነ</add>ቢር<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ስም፡ ወእም፡ ወምድር<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> 
                            ለኮከብኒ፡ ስም፡ ወእም<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ለገይስ፡ ስም፡ ወእም<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ወርኅ፡ ዕለት፡ በ፲ወ፮ ግድፍ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="chapters">
                    <label>Sixteen chapters</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ፩ ቀዳማዊ፡ ዐዐዐዐዐዐዐ አላዘያን፡ ዘወጽአ፡ ለሠናይ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ቤት፡ ቤተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወሕይወት፡ ወዝንቱ፡ ትእምርት፤ ኅሩይ፡ <sic>እሳቲዊ፡</sic> ወከዋክብት፡ አልመሻታሪ፡ 
                            <sic>ወእመዋዕል፡</sic> ሐሙስ፡ ወእግዚአብሔር፡ <sic>የአምር፡</sic> በአሰንዮ፡ ንብረት፡ ወኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት፡ ርቱዕ፡ ወብዙኅ፡ <sic>ፍሥሐ፡</sic> ወሐሤት፡ ወፍጻሜ፡ 
                            መፍቅድ፡ <sic>ወጸሕቅ፡</sic> <choice><sic>ወአግርር፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ወአግርሮ፡</corr></choice>
                            ፀላእት፤ <choice><sic>ወነጸሮ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ወነጽሮ፡</corr></choice> ሕልም፡ ወአስተጋብዖ፡ ሠናያት፡ እምለፌ፡ ወእምለፌ፡
                            ነጊደ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፡ ወፍጻሜ፡ ኵሉ፡ <sic>ተምኔታተ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied></sic>
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="henok">
                    <label>Untitled chapter</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet128">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 128</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አስማተ፡ ጭናቱ፡ ጮስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/>
                            ዘጸሐፍኩ፡ ለ<del rend="effaced" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ሄኖክ፡ <choice><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ኆኅያተ፡</corr><sic>ኆኅተ፡</sic></choice> 
                            ፊደል፡ ከማሁ፡ ጸሐፍ፡ ፀርየ፡ ወአርክየ፡ ሕይወትየ፡ ወእኩይየ፡ ሲሳይየ፡
                            <choice><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ወሐጕልየ፡</corr><sic>ወሐጉሉየ፡</sic></choice> <choice><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ክስት፡</corr><sic>ክሳት፡</sic></choice> ሊተ፡ 
                            <expan><abbr>ለገ</abbr><ex>ብርከ፡</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ዕ</abbr><ex>ገሌ፡</ex></expan>
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="kawakebt">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ ከዋክብት፡  ወመናዝል፡</foreign></label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Divinatory chapter on the planets and the lunar houses. Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ሐስበ፡ ከዋክብት፡ ወመናዝል፡ ለኮከብ፡ ስም፡ ወእም፡ ለአድባር፡ ስመ፡ ሀገር፡ ለሐራ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ዘመን፡ ከመ፡ ታዕምር፡ ላዕለ፡ እኪት፡ 
                            ወሠናይ፡ ስሞ፡ ወእሞ፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ፲ ወስክ፡ <choice><sic>በ ፳፷፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">በ ፳፰፡</corr></choice>
                            ግድፍ፡ ፩ አልሐመል፡ ኮከብ፡ ዘሚያዝያ፡ መስከረም፡ ራብዕ፡ ኆኅት፡ ስሙ፡ አድናኤል፡ ፀፀፀፀ፡ እሉ፡ ፬ ከዋክብት፡ ሰበ፡ ይሰርቁ፡ በራብዕ፡ ኆኅት፡ ለሰርቀት፡ ዘታጸንን፡ 
                            መስዓ፡ <choice><sic>ወይመጽእ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ወይወጽእ፡</corr></choice>
                            <sic>እምኒ<del rend="expunctuated">ሖ</del>ሃ፡</sic> ጠል፡ ወዝናም፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="helm">
                    <label>On the effect of dreams</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>The chapter is on the effect of dreams on individual days of the lunar month. Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet128">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 128</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            <choice><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ሐሳብ፡</corr><sic>ሐሰብ፡</sic></choice> በጨረቃው፡ 
                            ወራት፡ ሕልም፡ ያሳየው፡ የሚሆን፡ ነው፡ ያውቃል፡ በ፩ ጨረቃ፡ አምላክ፡ አዳምን፡ ካ፬ት፡ ፈጠረው፡ <sic>ኩሉ፡</sic>
                            ነገር፡ በጎ፡ ነው፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="mogad">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ ሞገድ፡</foreign>, or "Calculation of events"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ስመ፡ ባሕቲቱ፡ በበ፭<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ግድፍ፡ <choice><sic>፬</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">፩</corr></choice>
                            ንጉሥ፡ ሠናይ፡ ብዕል፡ ቀቲል፡ ፍቅ<del rend="expunctuated">ደ</del>ረ፡ ሰ<surplus>፡</surplus>ብእ፡ መደንግፅ፡ ሐሜት፡ ሀሎ፡ መልዕልተ፡ ርዕሱ፡ ጽሑፍ፡
                            ዓቢየ፡ <sic>ወብዓለ፡</sic> ጸጋ፡ ይከውን፡ ወሥራየ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ቦቱ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="nagar2">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez"><choice><sic>ሐሰበ፡</sic><corr resp="MV">ሐሳበ፡</corr></choice> ፪ ነገር፡</foreign>, or "Calculation of things. Two"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            <choice><sic>መፍቅሬ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">መፍቀሬ፡</corr></choice> ሕግ፡ ብዕል፡ ቀቲል፡ ሙቁሕ፡ ሀሎ፡
                            ጽሑፍ፡ በማዕከለ፡ ርእሱ፡ ዓቢየ፡ ወበዕለ፡ ጸጋ፡ ይከውን፡ ወሥራየ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ቦቱ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>    
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="negus">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ ንጉሥ፡</foreign>, or "Calculation the king"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ማኅተመ፡ ፍቅር፡ ብዕል፤ ቀቲል፡ <choice><sic>ፍናዊ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ፍናዌ፡</corr></choice>
                            ጽድቅ፡ ሀሎ፡ ጽሑፍ፡ መልዕልተ፡ ገጹ፡ ዓቢየ፡ ባዕለ፡ ክብር፤ ይከውን፡ ወሥራየ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ቦቱ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="nagar4">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ ፬ ነገር፡</foreign>, or "Calculation of things. Four"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            የዋህ፡ ብዕል፡ ነገረ፡ ቅንዓት፡ ኃይል፡ ቀቲል፡ ጽሑፍ፡ መልዕልተ፡ ርእሱ፡ ወባዕለ፡ ይከውን፡ ወሥራየ፡ ወይገብሩ፡ ቦቱ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="nagar5">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሀሳበ፡ ፭ ነገር፡</foreign>, or "Calculation (of things). Five"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet119">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth.119</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ንጉሥ፡ ብዕል፡ ሥራይ፡ ቀቲል፤ ፍቅር፤ ጥፍዓተ፤ ብእሲ፤ ሀሎ፤ ጽሑፍ፤ በማዕከለ፤ ርእሱ፤ <sic>ወሥራይ፤</sic> ይገብሩ፤ ቦቱ፤
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="asrab">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ አስራብ፡</foreign>, or "Calculation of the flowing waters"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet128">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 128</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ስመ፡ ወእመ፡ በበ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ፲ ግድፍ፡ ፩ ንጉሥ፡ አልጱስስ፡ ወሀብቱ፡ 
                            <sic>ሀብቱ፡</sic> ሀለወት፡ ተፈልጠ፡ እምላዕሌሁ፡ መንገለ፡
                            ምሥራቅ፡ ኢትመጽእ፡ ፍጡነ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="fenot">
                    <label><foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ ፍኖት፡</foreign>, or "Calculation of the paths"</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                        <note>Incipit taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet128">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 128</ref>.</note>
                        <ab>
                            ስምከ፡ ወእምከ፡ ወርኅ፡ ወዕለት፡ <choice><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ወንጌላዊ፡</corr><sic>ወንጌለዊ፡</sic></choice> 
                            በበ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="omitted">፡</t:supplied> ፲ ግድፍ፡ ፩ ሠናይ፡ ሖር፡ በነግህ፡ ወትረክብ፡
                            ብዙኃ፡ ዘሀለየ፡ ልብከ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>       
    </text></TEI>